Refund Policy

Effective Date: September 15, 2025

1. Eligibility
- Refunds are available for services not rendered or technical errors.
- Requests must be submitted within 30 days of the transaction.

2. Request Process
- Contact support with transaction details.
- Refund requests will be reviewed and confirmed via email.

3. Refund Methods
- Refunds are processed to the original payment method.
- Processing time may vary: 3-10 business days.

4. Exceptions
- Customized services or premium subscriptions may have different policies.
- Fraudulent or unauthorized transactions are handled separately.

5. Contact
Email: refunds@yourcompany.com
Phone: +1-800-555-1234
